window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Meeting during senior week on the day of their birthdays was pure coincidence.</b></p> <p>It was supposed to be nothing more for Lola Larson and TJ Kingston than three days of fake dating before going back to their everyday lives. Not thinking they will see each other again, they part ways without getting each other's last names or phone numbers.</p> <p>Two years later, they're in college, where they meet again. However, their priorities are different from the last time they saw each other.</p> <p>TJ wants nothing more than to enter the draft and play for the NBA. It's all he's worked hard for and has made sure that nothing and no one hinders him from achieving his dream. That is until he sees Lola again, and realizes that basketball is no longer his sole priority when he finds out he has a kid.</p>"; 
